<bibRefCitation box="[438,589,1669,1691]" pageId="1" pageNumber="114" refId="ref4240" refString="Gordon, R. D. (1976) The Scymnini of the United States and Canada: Key to genera and revision of Scymnus, Nephus and Diomus. Bulletin of the Buffalo Society of Natural Sciences, 28, 1 - 362." type="journal article">Gordon (1976)</bibRefCitation>
